translation.Name: Belgium Note - Ypres Military #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Ypres is no longer safe. DO NOT ENTER this area! Ypres is infested with zombies covered in radiation.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Make your way to the evacuation camp south from here immediately to be safe and secure from the virus.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: The Belgian Military is doing their best to keep the situation under control.
